208
00:13:11.948 --> 00:13:14.948
Kagazume sudah tewas.

209
00:13:14.948 --> 00:13:15.948
-Apa? -Apa?

210
00:13:15.948 --> 00:13:18.148
Dia sudah tewas ketika kau tiba di sana?

211
00:13:18.148 --> 00:13:19.648
Itu tidak masuk akal.

212
00:13:19.648 --> 00:13:21.948
Itu terlalu mudah!

213
00:13:21.948 --> 00:13:23.548
Kau benar.

214
00:13:24.648 --> 00:13:27.248
Tapi memang benar.

215
00:13:27.248 --> 00:13:29.648
Aku berlari,

216
00:13:29.648 --> 00:13:31.548
mencuci tumbler itu,

217
00:13:31.548 --> 00:13:33.448
dan membuangnya.

218
00:13:33.448 --> 00:13:35.748
Berhenti berpura-pura bodoh.

219
00:13:35.748 --> 00:13:39.148
Siapa lagi yang bisa membunuhnya?

220
00:13:40.648 --> 00:13:42.948
Mereka berdua...

221
00:13:42.948 --> 00:13:45.348
Tn. Mouri berpikir mereka mencurigakan?

222
00:13:45.348 --> 00:13:47.648
Tidak.

223
00:13:47.648 --> 00:13:50.648
Dia hanya ingin tahu apa mereka punya alibi.

224
00:13:50.648 --> 00:13:55.548
